modName: Windhelm Palace of the Kings player home
summary: Palace of the kings as a player home
descriptionHtml:
Also across the river from Riverwood, there is a building partially sunken into the ground, which leads to the Palace of the Player: a duplicate of Windhelm\'s Palace of the Kings converted into a player home.

I do take feature requests, so just leave a comment and I\'ll see what I can do!

Version 0.3
Added vendor \"Meredith\"
Fixed bugs that caused every container of the same type to contain the same items
Made the Ingot barrel in the jail/blacksmith area more...noticeable.

Version 0.2
Added a blacksmithing area to the barracks
Added some armor to the first room
Added a *functional* mapmarker
author: Hehooisbored
